{"tid":4741,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"人妻對出軌老公打槍 子彈意外射進睪丸","createTime":"2016-11-26T15:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T20:31:32.000Z","uid":12709,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d7065f9188591239060dee1af8e4817808c416d","tid":4741,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:27:32.000Z","msg":"美國佛羅里達州一名60歲婦人雷德(Victoria Reid)不滿丈夫欺騙她，偷偷在外面找小三，雷德在本周三拿起槍，對老公開火，結果子彈意外命中老公的一粒睪丸。<br />\n <br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，雷德發現老公出軌偷吃後，相當憤怒，在本周三強逼老公認錯。她先是要求老公坐在沙發上，然後拿起槍，要求老公承認出軌，並威脅要把老公「打到殘廢」，甚至說要瞄準他的臉部和胸腔開槍。<br />\n <br />\n之後雷德真的開槍，據悉原本雷德的目標是瞄準老公的膝蓋，但雷德卻打偏，子彈意外射進老公的睪丸。事發後雷德已遭到逮捕，據信她患有創傷後壓力症候群，而受傷的老公已在醫院治療，但未知目前的狀況。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"ba5452c37e067c427328e66f01852d8bdfb947af","tid":4741,"uid":4105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:31:04.000Z","msg":"粒子彈一定好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5d290c0dc6b8742fa2cdb26bfb25b4fa101adc","tid":4741,"uid":7683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:42:21.000Z","msg":"未入已經估到施旑婕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e549845646b2ea02d0902798757c2c1c2632b8f","tid":4741,"uid":17914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:49:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578c009e25511911b1f8f4d45798ff2419425b6d","tid":4741,"uid":1696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T16:08:20.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n我以為個人妻有鳩對住老公打j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1e7b215fc3a65e754a6aeeb03dd2c7eb433e3c","tid":4741,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T16:16:35.000Z","msg":"天命如此<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c785cbca234d838eac049dd75490fff54e4afe23","tid":4741,"uid":26797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-